\c 8
\s Vanezvuru zvina vanogutswa nechikafu naJesu
\p
\v 1 Namazuva iwayo zvakwakanga kune chaunga chikuru kwazvo, vasina chavangadya, Jesu akadanira vadzidzi vake kwaari, akati kwavari:
\v 2 Ndinetsitsi nechaunga; nokuti chadogara neni mazuva matatu vasina zvavangadya.
\v 3 Kana ndikavarega vaende kumba kwavo nenzara, vachaziya panzira; nokuti vamwe vavo vanobva kure.
\v 4 Vadzidzi vake vakamupindura, \add vakati\add*: Zvingabvepi zvingwa munhu zvaangagutsa nazvo ava murenje muno?
\v 5 Akavabvunza, \add akati\add*: Munezvingwa zvingani? Vakati: Zvinomwe.
\v 6 Zvino akaraira chaunga kuti chigare pasi pavhu; akatora zvingwa zvinomwe, akavonga, aka\add zvi\add*medura, ndokupa vadzidzi vake, kuti vaise pamberi \add pavo\add*; vakazviisa pamberi pechaunga.
\v 7 Uye vakanga vane hove duku shoma; zvino aka\add dzi\add*ropafadza, akati vadziise pamberi \add pavo\add*.
\v 8 Vakadya, vakaguta; ndokununga zvimedu zvakasara, matengu manomwe.
\v 9 Avo vakange vadya vainge vaiva zvuru zvina; akavarega vachienda.
\p
\v 10 Pakarepo akapinda muchikepe navadzidzi vake, akauya kumativi eDharimanuta.
\s Jesu unoramba kuratidza chiratidzo
\p
\v 11 Zvino vaFarisi vakabuda, vakatanga kupikisana naye, vachitsvaka kwaari chiratidzo chinobva kudenga, vachimuidza.
\v 12 Akagomera zvikuru pamweya wake akati: Zera iri rinotsvakirei chiratidzo? Zvirokwazvo ndinoti kwamuri: Hakuna chiratidzo chichapiwa kuzera iri.
\v 13 Ndokubva avasiya, akapindazve muchikepe, akabva akayambukira kumhiri.
\s Jesu unodudzira shoko rembiriso yavaFarisi navaSadhusi
\p
\v 14 Zvino vadzidzi vakanga vakangamwa kutora zvingwa; uye vakanga vasina navo \add chinhu\add* muchikepe kunze kwechingwa chimwe chete.
\v 15 Zvino akavaraira, achiti: Ngwarirai, muchenjere mbiriso yavaFarisi nembiriso yaHerodhe.
\v 16 Vakarangana pakati pavo vachiti: Nokuti hatina zvingwa.
\v 17 Zvino Jesu wakati achi\add zvi\add*ziva akati kwavari: Munorangana sei kuti hamuna zingwa? Hamusati maziva, kana kunzwisisa here? Muchine moyo mikukutu here?
\v 18 Mune meso hamuoni here? Uye mune nzeve, hamunzwi here? Uye hamurangariri here?
\v 19 Pandakamedurira vanezvuru zvishanu zvingwa zvishanu, matengu mangani azere nezvimedu amakanonga? Vakati kwaari: Gumi namaviri.
\v 20 Uye pazvinomwe pavanezvuru zvina, matengu mangani azere nezvimedu amakanonga? Ndokuti: Manomwe.
\v 21 Ndokubva ati kwavari: Seyi musinganzwisisi?
\s Jesu unosvinudza bofu paBhetisaidha
\p
\v 22 Zvino wakasvika kuBhetisaidha; vakauyisa bofu kwaari, vakamugombedzera kuti arinyangate.
\v 23 Akabata ruoko rwebofu, akaribudisira kunze komusha; akati apfira meso aro, akaisa maoko pamusoro paro, akaribvunza kana richiona chinhu.
\v 24 Ndokutarira kumusoro rikati: Ndinoona vanhu vakaita semiti, vachifamba.
\v 25 Mushure maizvozvo akaisazve maoko pamusoro pameso aro akaritaridza kumusoro, rikaporeswa, rikaona vose zvakajeka.
\v 26 Akarirega richienda kumba kwaro, achiti: Usapinda mumusha uye usaudza ani nani mumusha.
\s Petro unopupura kuti Jesu ndiye Kristu
\p
\v 27 Zvino Jesu akabuda navadzidzi vake vakaenda kumisha yeKesariya yeFiripi; vari munzira akabvunza vadzidzi vake achiti kwavari: Vanhu vanoti ndini ani?
\v 28 Vakapindura \add vachiti\add*: Johwani Mubhabhatidzi; asi vamwe: Eria; vamwezve: Umwe wavaporofita.
\v 29 Iye akati kwavari: Ko imwi munoti ndini ani? Petro akapindura akati kwaari: Imwi muri Kristu.
\v 30 Akavaraira zvikuru kuti varege kuudza munhu pamusoro pake.
\p
\v 31 Zvino akatanga kuvadzidzisa kuti Mwanakomana womunhu unofanira kutambudzika zvinhu zvizhinji nokurambwa navakuru, navapristi vakuru, navanyori, agourawa, uye mushure mamazuva matatu amukezve.
\v 32 Akataura shoko iro pachena. Zvino Petro akamutorera parutivi, akatanga kumutsiura.
\v 33 Asi iye atendeuka, ndokutarira vadzidzi vake, akatsiura Petro achiti: Ibva shure kwangu, Satani; nokuti haurangariri zvinhu zvaMwari, asi zvinhu zvavanhu.
\s Kutevera Jesu
\p
\v 34 Zvino wakati adanira kwaari chaunga navadzidzi vakewo, akati kwavari: Ani nani unoda kuuya shure kwangu, ngaazvirambe, atakure muchinjikwa wake, anditevere.
\v 35 Nokuti ani nani unoda kuponesa upenyu hwake, ucharashikirwa nahwo, asi ani nani ucharashikirwa noupenyu hwake nokuda kwangu nokweevhangeri, ndiye uchahuponesa.
\v 36 Nokuti zvinobatsirei munhu, kana akawana nyika yose akarashikirwa nomweya wake?
\v 37 Kana kuti munhu uchapei kuti adzikinure mweya wake?
\v 38 Nokuti ani nani unonyara pamusoro pangu napamashoko angu pazera iri roupombwe nokutadza, Mwanakomana womhunhu uchanyaravo pamusoro pake, paanouya mukubwinya kwaBaba vake navatumwa vatsvene.
